'''比利·克利福德·基摩亞'''（Billy Clifford Gilmour，{{bd|2001年|6月11日}}）是一名[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]職業足球員，現時被[[英超|英超]]球會[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切爾西]]外借至[[诺维奇城足球俱乐部|诺维奇城]]，主要司職[[中場|中場]]。代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]、[[蘇格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|蘇格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊]]參加國際比賽<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/02/11/billy-gilmour-on-moving-up-to-the-senior-squad-permanently|title=Billy Gilmour on moving up to the senior squad permanently {{!}} Official Site {{!}} Chelsea Football Club|website=ChelseaFC|access-date=2020-02-11|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305230318/https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2020/02/11/billy-gilmour-on-moving-up-to-the-senior-squad-permanently|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他此前為[[蘇超|蘇超]][[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]的青年梯隊球員，並在該球隊期間以年僅15歲之齡跟隨一線隊練習。基摩亞隨後拒絕格拉斯哥流浪給予的職業合約，在2017年加盟切爾西。

== 早年生活 ==
基摩亞在2001年6月11日出生於[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]，並在[[北艾爾郡|北艾爾郡]]{{link-en|阿德羅森|Ardrossan}}成長，其父親為前[[英國皇家海軍|英國皇家海軍]]士兵，並曾{{link-en|阿德羅森溫頓流浪足球俱樂部|Ardrossan Winton Rovers F.C.|阿德羅森溫頓流浪}}效力青年軍。基摩亞長大後曾分別入讀阿德羅森的斯坦利小學（Stanley Primary School）和[[基爾馬諾克|基爾馬諾克]]的{{link-en|格蘭奇學校|Grange Academy, Kilmarnock}}，並在就讀後者時參與[[蘇格蘭足球協會|蘇格蘭足球協會]]的足球員培訓計劃<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/scotland-and-chelseas-billy-gilmour-ahead-of-plan-but-remains-rooted-in-reality-zpvgw38cd |title=Scotland and Chelsea’s Billy Gilmour ‘ahead of plan’ but remains rooted in reality |first=Mark |last=Walker |newspaper=The Times |publisher= |date=16 October 2019 |accessdate=8 March 2020 |archive-date=2020-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321073921/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/scotland-and-chelseas-billy-gilmour-ahead-of-plan-but-remains-rooted-in-reality-zpvgw38cd |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 俱樂部生涯 ==
=== 格拉斯哥流浪 ===
基摩亞的職業生涯開始於[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]的青年軍，其進步使他迅速進入成年梯隊，並在2016年12月以17歲之齡於格拉斯哥流浪的U-20梯隊亮相，之後更在球隊主帥[[马克·沃伯顿|马克·沃伯顿]]的要求下與一線隊的球員一起訓練<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bairner |first1=Robin |title=Meet Rangers wonderkid Billy Gilmour: The starlet Chelsea have beaten Arsenal and Manchester United to |url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/meet-rangers-wonderkid-billy-gilmour-the-starlet-chelsea/a29cvw6htgq312yqnx019a5d1 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Goal.com |date=9 May 2017 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019220022/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/meet-rangers-wonderkid-billy-gilmour-the-starlet-chelsea/a29cvw6htgq312yqnx019a5d1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Billy Gilmour shares his delight after training with Rangers first team squad |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-youngster-billy-gilmour-shares-9687629 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Daily Record |date=25 January 2017 |location=Glasgow |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019220331/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-youngster-billy-gilmour-shares-9687629 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在沃伯頓離任後，基摩亞曾兩次被看守領隊{{link-en|格萊姆·穆蒂|Graeme Murty}}列進[[蘇格蘭足總盃|蘇格蘭足總盃]]的臨時陣容內<ref>{{cite news |title=Graeme Murty hopes Rangers can fend off interest from Chelsea in midfield star Billy Gilmour |url=https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/15198720.graeme-murty-hopes-rangers-can-fend-off-interest-from-chelsea-in-midfield-star-billy-gilmour/ |publisher=Glasgow Times |date=2017-04-03 |accessdate=2020-06-19 |archive-date=2020-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302201638/https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/15198720.graeme-murty-hopes-rangers-can-fend-off-interest-from-chelsea-in-midfield-star-billy-gilmour/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

格拉斯哥流浪下任領隊{{link-en|佩德羅·卡辛哈|Pedro Caixinha}}形容基摩亞是一位前途一片光明的球員，卡辛哈同時也與該球員的家人進行會談，試圖說服他續約<ref>{{cite news |last1=Newport |first1=Andy |title=Caixinha reveals he's met Billy Gilmour's parents in bid to keep ace at Rangers |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-boss-pedro-caixinha-reveals-10127591 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Daily Record |date=30 March 2017 |location=Glasgow |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026040938/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/rangers-boss-pedro-caixinha-reveals-10127591 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Gilmour set for Chelsea move – unless Gers succeed in last-ditch talks |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/transfers/rangers-hold-talks-with-billy-gilmour-chelsea-transfer-wonderkid-a7658371.html |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=The Independent |date=30 March 2017 |location=London |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410153019/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/transfers/rangers-hold-talks-with-billy-gilmour-chelsea-transfer-wonderkid-a7658371.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而在2017年5月時，格拉斯哥流浪宣佈基摩亞將加盟英超的[[車路士|車路士]]，轉會費未明，但據報金額非常巨大<ref>{{cite news |title=Rangers: Youth prospect Billy Gilmour opts for summer switch to Chelsea |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39858879 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=BBC Sport |date=9 May 2017 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903132723/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39858879 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[天空體育|天空體育]]報稱車路士支付了約50萬英鎊的初始費用，並可能根據球員的表現而進一步付款<ref>{{cite news |last1=Yew |first1=Oliver |title=Who is Chelsea new-boy Billy Gilmour? |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11096/10871035/who-is-chelsea-new-boy-billy-gilmour |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Sky Sports |date=10 May 2017 |language=en |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903074901/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11096/10871035/who-is-chelsea-new-boy-billy-gilmour |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[蘇格蘭足球協會|蘇格蘭足球協會]]的績效總監[[馬爾基·麥基|馬爾基·麥基]]曾向基摩亞和其家人建議，認為他應該留在格拉斯哥流浪以獲得更多的一線隊經驗。麥基還表示：「我真希望他（基摩亞）能夠快點被外借出去，讓他繼續進步下去」<ref>{{cite news |title=Malky Mackay: 'Billy Gilmour could have emulated Barry Ferguson at Rangers' |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40927422 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=BBC Sport |date=14 August 2017 |archive-date=2019-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114181848/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/40927422 |dead-url=no }}。</ref>。

=== 車路士 ===
[[File:Chelsea_7_Grimsby_1_(48798190337).jpg|200px]]對上[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|格林斯比镇]]時的基摩亞]]
基摩亞16歲生日後，於2017年7月正式與車路士簽約<ref>{{cite news |last1=Amako |first1=Uche |title=Billy Gilmour signs Chelsea contract two months after agreeing to leave Rangers |url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/824767/Chelsea-Transfer-News-Billy-Gilmour-professional-contract-Rangers-gossip-rumours |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Daily Express |date=4 July 2017 |location=London |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019221431/http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/824767/Chelsea-Transfer-News-Billy-Gilmour-professional-contract-Rangers-gossip-rumours |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他加入了「藍軍」的U-18梯隊，並在2017年9月對陣[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]青年軍的首秀中攻入一球<ref>{{cite news |last1=Forbes |first1=Craig |title=Billy Gilmour impresses in goalscoring Chelsea debut |url=http://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/billy-gilmour-impresses-in-goalscoring-chelsea-debut-1-4556555 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=The Scotsman |date=11 September 2017 |location=Edinburgh |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019220316/http://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/billy-gilmour-impresses-in-goalscoring-chelsea-debut-1-4556555 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也在此後的兩場比賽中有所進帳<ref>{{cite news |last1=McDougall |first1=Mark |title=Former Rangers kid Billy Gilmour scores third goal in three games for Chelsea |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/former-rangers-kid-billy-gilmour-11264590 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Daily Record |date=30 September 2017 |location=Glasgow |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019221045/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/former-rangers-kid-billy-gilmour-11264590 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年7月，17歲的基摩亞與車路士簽署了他的第一份職業合約<ref>{{cite news |title=Billy Gilmour: Former Rangers youth signs first professional contract at Chelsea |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44723798 |accessdate=7 August 2018 |work=BBC Sport |date=5 July 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705094015/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44723798 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

新上任的主帥[[法蘭克·蘭帕德|法蘭克·蘭帕德]]在2019年7月10日友賽對陣[[波希米亞人足球俱樂部|波希米亞人]]的比賽派遣基摩亞上場，使後者達成其一線隊的首秀<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bryce |first1=Liam |title=Billy Gilmour makes Chelsea debut as ex-Rangers prospect given the nod |url=https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/billy-gilmour-makes-chelsea-debut-17846062 |accessdate=10 July 2019 |work=Daily Record |date=10 July 2019 |location=Glasgow |archive-date=2019-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710212025/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/billy-gilmour-makes-chelsea-debut-17846062 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[2019年歐洲超級盃|2019年歐洲超級盃]]則是基摩亞第一次出現在正賽的大名單上，他沒有替補上場，該場比賽他們雖在[[加時賽|加時]]以2–2逼和[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]，但在[[點球大戰|點球大戰]]中「藍軍」僅得4球，對手則有5球，最終車路士以總比數6–7落敗<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/match/2025638--liverpool-vs-chelsea/lineups/?iv=true|title=Liverpool-Chelsea <nowiki>|</nowiki> Line-ups <nowiki>|</nowiki> UEFA-Super Cup|website=[[UEFA|UEFA]]|accessdate=9 June 2020|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612075840/https://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/match/2025638--liverpool-vs-chelsea/lineups/?iv=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

基摩亞的第一次英超亮相是在2019年8月31日對陣[[錫菲聯|錫菲聯]]的比賽上，於84分鐘替補[[塔米·亚伯拉罕|塔米·亚伯拉罕]]上場。而在[[英足盃|英足盃]]面對[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|格林斯比镇]]的比賽則是他的第一次首發<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/49736854|title=Chelsea 7–1 Grimsby Town: Reece James impresses on debut|date=2019-09-25|access-date=2019-09-25|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925230119/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/49736854|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年2月，基摩亞獲提升到車路士的一線隊<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51466510 |title=Billy Gilmour: Chelsea midfielder now with first team full time |website=BBC Sport |publisher= |date=11 February 2020 |accessdate=13 February 2020 |archive-date=2020-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212140708/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51466510 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2–0戰勝利物浦的[[足總盃|足總盃]]比賽上表現大受好評<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51728140 |title=Billy Gilmour: Chelsea's Scottish teenager 'incredible' in Liverpool win |first=Thomas |last=Duncan |website=BBC Sport |date=4 March 2020 |accessdate=5 March 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926175921/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51728140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 诺维奇城 ===
2021年7月，基摩亞租借加盟至[[英超|英超]]俱樂部[[诺维奇城足球俱乐部|诺维奇城]]為期一個賽季。<ref>{{cite news |title=Norwich sign Chelsea's Gilmour on loan |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57692813 |access-date=2021-07-02 |work=BBC Sport |date=2021-07-02 |archive-date=2021-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702102205/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57692813 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 國家隊生涯 ==
基摩亞在2016年被選進蘇格蘭U16的陣容內，參加{{link-en|勝利盾|Victory Shield}}賽事<ref>{{cite news |title=Under-16 Victory Shield squad announced |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=1848&newsID=16580 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |publisher=Scottish FA |date=20 October 2016 |language=en |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019164909/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/scottish_fa_news.cfm?page=1848&newsID=16580 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年8月，基摩亞對上意大利U-17的友賽中首次為蘇格蘭U17上陣，並在兩天後為射入一球，助球隊以2–1擊敗英格蘭U-17<ref>{{cite news |title=Billy Gilmour – U17 squad matches |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=1848&playerID=224107&squadID=13 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |publisher=Scottish FA |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019220343/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=1848&playerID=224107&squadID=13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ex-Rangers wonderkid Billy Gilmour scores as Scotland U17s are beaten by England |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-match-reports/former-rangers-youngster-billy-gilmour-11022741 |accessdate=19 October 2017 |work=Daily Record |date=20 August 2017 |location=Glasgow |archive-date=2019-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114084930/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-match-reports/former-rangers-youngster-billy-gilmour-11022741 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

基摩亞的[[蘇格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|蘇格蘭U21]]首次亮相在2018年[[土倫盃國際足球錦標賽|土倫盃國際足球錦標賽]]對陣[[法國21歲以下國家足球隊|法國U21]]的比賽中出現，該場賽事他們以1–0戰勝對手<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news/scotland-stun-hosts-france-to-record-toulon-win/?rid=13925 |title=Scotland stun hosts France to record Toulon win |publisher=Scottish Football Association |date=30 May 2018 |accessdate=31 May 2018 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609143529/https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news/scotland-stun-hosts-france-to-record-toulon-win/?rid=13925 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。以殿軍結束錦標賽後，基摩亞獲頒最具突破球員獎<ref name="BP">{{cite news |title=Individual awards for Billy Gilmour and Michael Johnston seal successful Toulon trip |url=https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news/individual-awards-for-billy-gilmour-and-michael-johnston-seal-successful-toulon-trip/?rid=14258 |accessdate=10 June 2018 |publisher=Scottish Football Association |date=10 June 2018 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609143511/https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/news/individual-awards-for-billy-gilmour-and-michael-johnston-seal-successful-toulon-trip/?rid=14258 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年5月19日，基摩亞被列入[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭隊]]26人陣容，參加[[2020年歐洲足球錦標賽|2020年歐洲國家盃]]，這是他首次入選成年隊。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://theathletic.com/news/scotland-euro-2020-squad-gilmour/wNnv1TaJ1CV1|title=Scotland include Chelsea’s Billy Gilmour in Euro 2020 squad|website=The Athletic|date=2021-05-19|accessdate=2021-05-19|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519131422/https://theathletic.com/news/scotland-euro-2020-squad-gilmour/wNnv1TaJ1CV1|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月2日，他在對陣[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]的友誼賽中在第81分鐘替補出場，完成了成年代表隊處子秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2021/06/02/billy-gilmour-makes-scotland-debut-in-netherlands-draw|title=BILLY GILMOUR MAKES SCOTLAND DEBUT IN NETHERLANDS DRAW|website=Chelsea FC|date=2021-06-03|accessdate=2021-06-03|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607070907/https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2021/06/02/billy-gilmour-makes-scotland-debut-in-netherlands-draw|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年6月18日，基摩亞在[[2020年歐洲國家盃|2020年歐洲國家盃]]蘇格蘭對上[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]0-0平局的比賽表現十分出色，当选[[海尼根|海尼根]]欧國杯之星。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Midfielder Billy Gilmour expresses his pride as Scotland hold England at Wembley |url=https://www.bt.com/sport/news/2021/june/midfielder-billy-gilmour-expresses-his-pride-as-scotland-hold-england-at-wembley|access-date=2021-06-18|publisher= BT Sport}}</ref>

